<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c1">"ضعيف"</span>. <span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(٤/ ٢٨٩)</span>، و<span class="c1">"اللسان"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ٦٨٦)</span>.<span class="c5"> ترجمة:</span> إسماعيل بن يزيد القطان. و<span class="c1">"الدراية"</span> <span class="c2">(١)</span> <span class="c2">(٢/ ٢٤٥)</span>.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c1">"منكر الحديث"</span>. <span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ١٦٤)</span>.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c1">"متروك"</span>. <span class="c1">"الفتح"</span> <span class="c2">(٤/ ١٦)</span>، و<span class="c1">"التلخيص"</span> <span class="c2">(١/ ١١٤، ٢/ ٨٤، ٥٥٣)</span>.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">١٢٣٤) عمر بن محمد بن زيد بن عبد الله بن عمر بن الخطاب المدني:</span> ثقة <span class="c2">(خ م د س ق)</span>.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
